### Registrar un usuario
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "user1@gmail.com",
    "password": "123456",
    "confirmPassword": "123456"
}

### iniciar sesión para obtener token
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "user1@gmail.com",
    "password": "123456"
}

### verificar token
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/verify
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6MjUsImVtYWlsIjoidXNlcjVAZ21haWwuY29tIiwiaWF0IjoxNzcxNTE4MjA5LCJleHAiOjE3NzE2MDQ2MDl9.5d7cmArSn8_uKWfgSRhmyUr7W41HlmBYTE-n_bggnHU


### crear una task
POST http://localhost:8000/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer Token

{
    "title": "Nueva tarea2",
    "description": "Descripción de la nueva tarea",
    "priority": "Alta",
    "limit_date": "2024-07-15T12:00:00Z",
    "user_id": "2"
}

### obtener todas las tasks de un usuario
GET http://localhost:8000/tasks/tasksUser/1
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6MSwiZW1haWwiOiJ1c2VyMUBnbWFpbC5jb20iLCJpYXQiOjE3NzIxMjA1NTcsImV4cCI6MTc3MjIwNjk1N30.DtVDWIplLLLzNsy2xM4XXEY_X7rQJpI4r5NChTAj2p8

